text.tspan: Handles all related to the Terrain object
Handles functions to alter terrain mesh/appearance
Apply filters: Square Padding; Arch; Pixelate;
Clamp Height To Range; Custom Curves
Terrain Color: Height Color; Normal Color, Smooth Color
and handles all of its interactions
Contain information relevant to the game mechanics
Handles placement and tracking of player buildings
Items can be buildings, owned by the player or not,
that are relevant to the game mechanics
